                     <interp inst="t18241202-142-person906" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I saw the shawl hanging at the door; the prisoner stood within the door-cill, unpinned the shawl, and walked away. I went after him, and he threw it down.<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182412020068"></xptr>Charles Edwards pursued him, and while I was stooping to pick it up, he cried Stop thief! - I left the shawl and took the prisoner.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I am in great distress.</p>
